We believe that we have the following strengths:
• Favourable macroeconomic environment and supportive household
  growth;
• Vertically integrated operating platform run by a highly successful
  management team;
• Leading position in the attractive Central European market with
  high barriers to entry;
• Attractive and well-maintained residential portfolio;
• Diversified residential portfolio with broad demographic appeal
  and stable tenant base;
• Strong and contracted rental growth driven by rent deregulation;
  and
• Strong operating performance underpinned by a conservative
  capital structure.
Our strategy is composed of the following elements:
• Achieve revenue growth through contracted increases in
  post-regulated rents and re-leasing vacant units at market rates;
• Increase occupancy rates;
• Continue to optimise our tenant base;

